content:
### Haiku

Whispers of seasons,  
Trees don cloaks of time's colors,  
Nature's dance unfolds.

### Table: Seasonal Comparison in Temperate Deciduous Forest

| Season     | Average Temperature (°C) | Average Precipitation (mm) |
|------------|---------------------------|----------------------------|
| Spring     | 10 - 15                   | 75 - 125                   |
| Summer     | 20 - 25                   | 100 - 150                  |
| Autumn     | 10 - 15                   | 50 - 100                   |
| Winter     | -5 - 5                    | 25 - 75                    |

### HTML and CSS Code Example

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
            color: #004d40;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .haiku {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            font-style: italic;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        table {
            margin: 0 auto;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            width: 80%;
        }
        th, td {
            border: 1px solid #004d40;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        th {
            background-color: #e0f7fa;
        }
        td {
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
    </style>
    <title>Haiku and Season Comparison</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="haiku">Whispers of seasons, Trees don cloaks of time's colors, Nature's dance unfolds.</div>
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th>Season</th>
            <th>Average Temperature (°C)</th>
            <th>Average Precipitation (mm)</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Spring</td>
            <td>10 - 15</td>
            <td>75 - 125</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Summer</td>
            <td>20 - 25</td>
            <td>100 - 150</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Autumn</td>
            <td>10 - 15</td>
            <td>50 - 100</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Winter</td>
            <td>-5 - 5</td>
            <td>25 - 75</td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
```
